headline: Cutter Law and Almeida Law Group File Lawsuit Alleging Unlawful 'Junk Fees' on Cal Parks' Reservation Site, Oakland, California - May 8, 2025
summary: OAKLAND, Calif., May 8, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- Plaintiffs filed a class action lawsuit challenging what they allege are unlawful 'junk fees' charged on the California Department of Parks and Recreation...
